# ❤️ Heart Disease Prediction using Deep Learning

## 1. Introduction

### Project Overview

Heart disease remains one of the leading causes of mortality worldwide. Early detection using Artificial Intelligence can support healthcare professionals in making accurate and timely decisions.

This project presents a complete Deep Learning pipeline for predicting heart disease by utilizing:

* ECG signal analysis
* Clinical patient data
* CNN-based feature extraction
* CNN-LSTM hybrid architecture
* Multi-modal fusion learning
* Explainable AI using SHAP

