# 3. Dataset Collection

## 3.1 MIT-BIH ECG Dataset

The ECG dataset is collected using the WFDB package and contains:

* Raw ECG waveforms
* Annotation files
* Heartbeat labels
* R-peak information

### Main Tasks

* Download ECG records
* Read signal files
* Load annotations
* Analyze heartbeat categories

